 * PATCH v2:
 * 6) Patient vs employee name cross-check now consumed from employe_data.
 * 7) decision.status / rationale from upstream node now consumed.
 * 8) patientEmployeeNameMatch === false is a hardFail in dataConsistency.
 * 9) upstreamForcesManualReview adds softWarn and guarantees score >= 50.
 * 10) decisionRationale lines surfaced as danger bullets in groupsHIGH.
